---Genymotion Emulator Setup---

1. Install Genymotion + Virtual Box
2. Open Genymotion 
3. Click Create to create a new virtual device
4. Choose: Device- Google Pixel 6
           Android API Version- Android 11.0
5. Name it AndroidWorldAvd and finish the setup
6. Run the device to view the virtual device.

--Tip--
In order to confirm that it is working properly when you later download Anaconda, open the PowerShell and run this command: "adb devices". You should be able to see the Genymotion device listed there. 
